54:50.411 --> 54:52.245
[DISTANT FOOTSTEPS]

57:48.612 --> 57:51.775
Hey, your pals,
they all left.

57:51.777 --> 57:54.878
I haven't seen any of them
for days now.

57:57.344 --> 58:00.875
Aren't you pissed
that they just left you here

58:00.877 --> 58:02.578
all by yourself, huh?

58:05.812 --> 58:09.779
Now you and I are the same.

58:11.777 --> 58:13.379
We're alone.

58:20.277 --> 58:21.443
Ah.

58:21.445 --> 58:24.010
- Sorry.
- [GATE RATTLES]

58:24.012 --> 58:25.642
Hey!

58:25.644 --> 58:28.309
I didn't do it on purpose.

58:28.311 --> 58:30.843
Why are you always sulking?
Come on, hey.

58:30.845 --> 58:33.476
Come on, smile, for fuck's sake.
Make an effort.

58:33.478 --> 58:36.408
You know what your problem is?
You're such a fucking bore.

58:36.410 --> 58:38.375
You don't know how to have fun.

58:38.377 --> 58:40.909
Your kids must've been thrilled
that you were never around.

58:40.911 --> 58:44.543
One day I'm gonna get sick of
all this and get out of here,

58:44.545 --> 58:47.375
and you'll be left all alone
like an asshole.

58:47.377 --> 58:49.875
And you can't even die because
you're just gonna stay here,

58:49.877 --> 58:51.810
and you'll regret these moments.

58:51.812 --> 58:54.642
You're gonna think to yourself,
"Why did I let him go?"

58:54.644 --> 58:56.010
But it'll be too late

58:56.012 --> 58:59.276
